item.title: Files
item.description:
Dell Axim X5 Windows Mobile 2003 Upgrade

This will upgrade your Dell Axim X5 PDA to Windows Mobile 2003. It can also back up your current software version. I have not been able to find this anywhere else.



Download the Dell Axim X5 Windows Mobile 2003 Upgrade

HP iPAQ HX2000 Series Windows Mobile 6.5 ROM

This is Spiaatie's Windows Mobile 6.5.3 ROM for the HP iPAQ HX2000 series. It works just fine on my HX2795b. This ROM is very hard to find, and I haven't been able to find it anywhere else.

item.title: Wallpapers
item.description:
The Ultimate macOS Wallpaper Archive

This archive includes every default macOS default wallpaper, in original quality, ripped straight from real Macs. Every wallpaper from Cheetah to Ventura is included. All 3 versions of the default Mojave Desert and Catalina wallpapers are included (day, night, live.)


Download The Ultimate OS X Wallpaper Archive (Google Drive)

Dell XPS Windows Vista OEM Wallpapers

These are all of the default desktop wallpapers included with a Dell XPS computer with Windows Vista, including the Microsoft default ones and some Dell/XPS specific ones. Taken from the restore disc of an XPS M1530.
